It's a review.

01:04:22.330 --> 01:04:24.770
And the title of the review
is neural innervation

01:04:24.770 --> 01:04:28.700
of white adipose tissue and
the control of lipolysis.

01:04:28.700 --> 01:04:30.830
That's neural innervation
of white adipose tissue

01:04:30.830 --> 01:04:32.340
and the control of lipolysis.

