other labs showing that,

01:41:38.450 --> 01:41:40.310
when you look at different diets,

01:41:40.310 --> 01:41:41.990
you look at low fat diets,

01:41:41.990 --> 01:41:43.110
high fat diets,

01:41:43.110 --> 01:41:45.543
keto diets, intermittent fasting,

01:41:46.970 --> 01:41:49.340
provided people stick to
their particular diet,

01:41:49.340 --> 01:41:52.700
it doesn't really matter
which diet you follow.

