'cause it facilitates
the transition to sleep.

01:42:41.760 --> 01:42:43.820
That's what works for me.

01:42:43.820 --> 01:42:46.730
But when insulin is low,

01:42:46.730 --> 01:42:51.730
you do place your system in a
position to oxidize more fat.

01:42:52.120 --> 01:42:54.760
And so that's why I think a
lot of people do see benefit

01:42:54.760 --> 01:42:57.940
from lower carbohydrate or
moderate carbohydrate diets,

01:42:57.940 --> 01:42:59.440
because when insulin is low,

01:42:59.440 --> 01:43:02.300
you are in a position to oxidize more fat.

