01:46:23.430 --> 01:46:26.370
Can slightly reduce blood glucose.

01:46:26.370 --> 01:46:28.740
I can slightly increase HDLC,

01:46:28.740 --> 01:46:31.490
the good form of the blood lipid

01:46:31.490 --> 01:46:34.020
and slightly reduce overall cholesterol.

01:46:34.020 --> 01:46:38.200
And as I mentioned, it can slightly modify

01:46:38.200 --> 01:46:40.150
the pathway involving glucagon,

01:46:40.150 --> 01:46:41.890
such that you get a considerable effect,

01:46:41.890 --> 01:46:44.060
not a huge effect on fat oxidation,

01:46:44.060 --> 01:46:46.710
so it can improve pat oxidation rates.

01:46:46.710 --> 01:46:48.090
It has a number of other effects,

01:46:48.090 --> 01:46:51.650
some of which I talked
during the month on hormones

01:46:51.650 --> 01:46:53.750
and that sort of thing.

01:46:53.750 --> 01:46:57.120
It has strong effects
on rates of pregnancy

01:46:57.120 --> 01:46:58.190
and sperm quality.

