So clearly carnitine is doing
lots of different things

01:47:00.470 --> 01:47:02.060
and lots of different cells.

01:47:02.060 --> 01:47:04.020
It's impacting sperm motility.

01:47:04.020 --> 01:47:07.090
They're in a large number
