01:47:07.090 --> 01:47:09.560
Slight reductions in blood pressure

01:47:09.560 --> 01:47:12.732
and has these interesting
effects on reducing fatigue

01:47:12.732 --> 01:47:14.100
during exercise,

01:47:14.100 --> 01:47:17.040
reducing inflammatory
markers like interleukin 6.

01:47:17.040 --> 01:47:19.870
So it has a number of
effects that on the whole

01:47:19.870 --> 01:47:22.760
are quote unquote positive
or at least in the direction

01:47:22.760 --> 01:47:24.200
